{"tid":1717295,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【禁藥風波】孫楊聽證會周五展開　敗訴恐被禁賽8年 (18:53)","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T14:41:05.000Z","uid":225130,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5191d06b8aecf1e1e69eb468f0536d8ac2b12313","tid":1717295,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"中國隊飛魚孫楊涉拒藥檢一案，國際體育仲裁法庭（CAS）周五將於瑞士舉行聽證會，《美聯社》今日引述消息，指CAS接到世界反禁藥組織（WADA）要求，孫楊一旦敗訴，要求判他2至8年禁賽。<br />\n<br />\n孫楊於去年9月被指拒絕藥檢，其保鑣涉用鐵鎚打破尿液樣本玻璃瓶。WADA因國際泳聯拒罰孫楊，提告至國際體育仲裁法庭，周五於瑞士展開聽證會。美聯社今日報道，WADA向CAS要求，一旦孫楊敗訴，禁賽期需介乎2年至8年，或令這名奧運3金得主，錯過明年東京奧運。<br />\n<br />\n聽證會在當地時間早上展開，自1999年後首次容許公眾旁聽，並設網上直播，全程約12小時，但不會即場有判決。據報孫楊的代表律師已出發瑞士，而聽證會主席是意大利前外長弗拉蒂尼。"},{"pid":"42f18f098f0ef829ae049da6e8d2a9f88e336774","tid":1717295,"uid":96941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾抵喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17c94742812bd4f4d499dbfcc2abd308822cfb7","tid":1717295,"uid":215089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:43:46.000Z","msg":"尿紫楊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151707d3cb11ccd248793ac62e30c5d469433fb4","tid":1717295,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"42f18f098f0ef829ae049da6e8d2a9f88e336774","tid":1717295,"uid":96941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾抵喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"希望佢停2年"},{"pid":"d1d4f855b59cd7e097216e150082cbf5cf44ab7a","tid":1717295,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"151707d3cb11ccd248793ac62e30c5d469433fb4","tid":1717295,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"42f18f098f0ef829ae049da6e8d2a9f88e336774","tid":1717295,"uid":96941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:42:27